---
---
<section class="about-scene">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="scene-content">
      <div class="label">Manifesto</div>
      <h1 class="title">Engineering <em>Performance.</em></h1>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="p-wrap">
          <p>We believe that growth is a technical challenge, not just a creative one. Our studio was built to solve the fragmentation in the ecommerce ecosystem.</p>
          <p>By unifying design, engineering, and data, we deliver stores that aren't just beautiful—they're highly efficient revenue tools.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-list">
          <div class="value-item">
            <span class="num">01</span>
            <span class="txt">Speed is Paramount</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <span class="num">02</span>
            <span class="txt">Data over Assumptions</span>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <span class="num">03</span>
            <span class="txt">Systems over One-offs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="focus-scroller">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="focus-head">
      <div class="label">Expertise</div>
      <h2 class="title">Strategic <em>Industries.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="focus-grid-main">
      <a href="/enfoque-salud" class="focus-box">
        <span class="box-num">01</span>
        <h3>Enfoque en Salud</h3>
        <p>Technical architecture for high-stakes health brands.</p>
        <div class="box-link">Go to Page //</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/enfoque-legal" class="focus-box">
        <span class="box-num">02</span>
        <h3>Enfoque Legal</h3>
        <p>Trusted digital infrastructure for elite law firms.</p>
        <div class="box-link">Go to Page //</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/enfoque-pymes" class="focus-box">
        <span class="box-num">03</span>
        <h3>Enfoque Emprendedore/PYMES</h3>
        <p>Scalable growth engines for small and medium businesses.</p>
        <div class="box-link">Go to Page //</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/enfoque-retail" class="focus-box">
        <span class="box-num">04</span>
        <h3>Enfoque Retail/Mayoristas</h3>
        <p>Complex B2B and B2C infrastructure for scale.</p>
        <div class="box-link">Go to Page //</div>
      </a>
      <a href="/enfoque-marca-personal" class="focus-box">
        <span class="box-num">05</span>
        <h3>Enfoque Marca Personal</h3>
        <p>Authority building and digital systems for experts.</p>
        <div class="box-link">Go to Page //</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-scene {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 120px 0;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--void);
  }
  .scene-content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }
  .label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .title {
    font-family: var(--title);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .title em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--teal);
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 80px;
  }
  .p-wrap p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--smoke);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .values-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }
  .value-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rim);
  }
  .value-item:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rim);
  }
  .num {
    font-family: var(--title);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--teal);
  }
  .txt {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }
  .focus-scroller {
    padding: 120px 0;
    background: var(--void);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rim);
  }
  .focus-head { margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .focus-grid-main {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .focus-box {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--rim);
    padding: 40px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.4s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .focus-box:hover {
    border-color: var(--teal);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    background: var(--teal-glow);
  }
  .box-num {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .focus-box h3 {
    font-family: var(--title);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .focus-box p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--smoke);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .box-link {
    font-family: var(--title);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-top: auto;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
    .focus-grid-main {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
